{"tid":2514094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稅務局今日發出約262萬份報稅表","createTime":"2021-05-03T04:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T05:42:20.000Z","uid":52779,"like":9,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"7f507444eeba1cd154c95663fcad67a78454d184","tid":2514094,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"稅務局今日發出約262萬份2020/21課稅年度報稅表，一般而言，納稅人須於1個月內，即6月3日或之前交報稅表。經營獨資業務人士的交表限期為3個月，即8月3日或之前，網上報稅可自動獲延期1個月。<br />\n<br />\n立法會上月底通過《2021年收入（稅務寬免）條例草案》，落實政府在預算案提出的稅務寬免，即寬減20/21年度百分之百的薪俸稅、個人入息課稅和利得稅，每宗個案以10000元為上限。<br />\n<br />\n由今日至7月2日期間，稅務局延長電話查詢熱線187 8022的服務時間，以解答有關報稅的查詢，星期一至五延長至下午7時，星期六由上午9時至下午1時，星期日及公眾假期休息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588962-20210503.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588962-20210503.htm&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=ddbc19ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588962-20210503.htm&h=53e44822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588962-20210503.htm</a>"},{"pid":"67010a4427885825c308d56fd68b08ec23d81ce9","tid":2514094,"uid":281492,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae31f944009ddd7c246a46babafcdad983481f8b","tid":2514094,"uid":7323,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:46:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">屌你老母</span>"},{"pid":"01